{"author":{"id":"783b610f274a0d93f6239db0fc75d0982606c877a4661d3aea84b42bc3a85cea"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1513031741,"nonce":"fhEH1iDyp4DsCUed4g7tTSbvwlA=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyODExOTE0OTc=","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/1630","origin":"github"},"title":"GetFastaBed fails to retrieve data for non-DM genomes","message":"Tool is looking for input where it will not exist for any genome created without a DM. More details below with error/command-line. \n\n**Tool**: GetFastaBed v 2.26.0.0 (updated 2017-07-05, IUC tool)\n\n**Tool repo**: https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/iuc/bedtools/b73962f8fcbf\n\n**Test history, mm10 + mm9 fail, hg38 success, all success with Extract**: https://usegalaxy.org/u/jen/h/test-history-getfastabed\n\n**Command line for successful hg38**\n`bedtools getfasta     -fi '/galaxy/data/hg38/seq/hg38.fa' -bed '/galaxy-repl/main/files/020/919/dataset_20919268.dat' -fo '/galaxy-repl/main/files/020/919/dataset_20919271.dat'`\n\n**Command line for UNsuccessful mm9**\n`bedtools getfasta     -fi '/galaxy/data/mm9/seq/mm9.fa' -bed '/galaxy-repl/main/files/020/919/dataset_20919426.dat' -fo '/galaxy-repl/main/files/020/919/dataset_20919491.dat'`\n\n**Error for UNsuccessful mm9**\n```\nFatal error: Exit code 1 ()\nindex file /galaxy/data/mm9/seq/mm9.fa.fai not found, generating...\ncould not open index file /galaxy/data/mm9/seq/mm9.fa.fai for writing!\n```\n\nThe file 'mm9.fa.fai' will not exist in this location (will be nested under /galaxy/data/mm9/samtools) for any genome not created with a Data Manager. Non-DM data is most of the content at http://usegalaxy.org.\n\nExtract is fine because it accesses the loc for 2bit data.\n\n**UPDATE: Moved from https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/issues/4412** See comments there for @mvdbeek proposed fix (change tool to use symlinks)","files":null}]}